on the mountains♪

579
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:49,470
♪The clouds conceal sins♪

580
00:28:49,690 --> 00:28:55,550
♪One thought ruins everything for all♪

581
00:28:55,920 --> 00:28:59,510
♪The wind and moon
fall through our fingers♪

582
00:28:59,510 --> 00:29:02,670
♪Like a dream that will return
to the starry night♪

583
00:29:02,790 --> 00:29:05,550
♪The illusion is full of lies♪

584
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:09,740
♪Turning into cycles flowing in time♪

585
00:29:09,740 --> 00:29:13,050
♪Listen to the falling leaves
playing a sad song♪

586
00:29:13,260 --> 00:29:16,940
♪In the cold wind, part with me♪

587
00:29:17,140 --> 00:29:19,770
♪The ones cast aside♪

588
00:29:19,770 --> 00:29:22,900
♪Have nowhere to belong♪

589
00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:04,180
Father.

590
00:31:05,660 --> 00:31:06,500
Jingming,

591
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:07,980
