593
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:10,500
Yanyan is fine.

594
00:31:10,700 --> 00:31:11,540
Father, don't worry.

595
00:31:14,990 --> 00:31:17,260
Shen Qilan should be in prison.

596
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:19,140
Why did she show up at Rain Chamber?

597
00:31:19,620 --> 00:31:20,460
Father,

598
00:31:20,890 --> 00:31:22,700
I've questioned the jailers.

599
00:31:23,580 --> 00:31:24,900
They were all drugged.

600
00:31:25,740 --> 00:31:27,220
How could a fragile woman

601
00:31:27,660 --> 00:31:29,020
like her drug the jailers

602
00:31:29,020 --> 00:31:30,380
and escape from the prison?

603
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:33,660
Was there no one to help her?

604
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:35,020
Father,

605
00:31:35,740 --> 00:31:37,900
she is skilled in manipulating men.

606
00:31:38,580 --> 00:31:39,420
I married her

607
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:41,980
because she enchanted me back then.

608
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:43,260
That night,

609
00:31:43,700 --> 00:31:45,820
I did visit her in prison,

610
00:31:46,260 --> 00:31:47,100
but I found her

611
00:31:47,340 --> 00:31:49,060
exchanging glances with the jailers.

612
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:51,900
So, she must have

613
00:31:52,060 --> 00:31:53,300
used this trick again

614
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:54,740
to slip away unnoticed.

615
00:31:57,460 --> 00:31:58,300
Jingming,

616
00:31:58,660 --> 00:31:59,620
protect Yanyan.

617
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:02,020
I won't forgive anyone who dares

618
00:32:02,340 --> 00:32:03,540
to harm my grandson.

619
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:04,540
Yes.

620
00:32:10,660 --> 00:32:11,660
Jingxiu,

621
00:32:12,820 --> 00:32:14,100
your cap is crooked.

622
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:31,700
Qilan,

623
00:32:32,860 --> 00:32:34,040
I've never looked down on you

624
00:32:34,540 --> 00:32:35,980
because you were

625
00:32:36,460 --> 00:32:37,400
a concubine's daughter.

626
00:32:39,260 --> 00:32:41,100
I've always regarded you as my sister.

627
00:32:42,540 --> 00:32:44,340
As your elder sister,

628
00:32:45,180 --> 00:32:46,860
I failed to guide you in time.

629
00:32:48,110 --> 00:32:49,440
None of this is your fault.

630
00:32:55,060 --> 00:32:56,380
Qilan, do you know?

631
00:32:57,100 --> 00:32:58,100
(Tomb of Shen Qilan)

632
00:32:58,100 --> 00:32:59,180
In your heart,

633
00:33:00,260 --> 00:33:01,820
you valued your background too much.

634
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:05,220
You thought that others would look down

635
00:33:05,620 --> 00:33:07,100
on your background.

636
00:33:09,540 --> 00:33:10,820
I hope in the next life,

637
00:33:12,060 --> 00:33:13,420
we can live in a world

638
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:16,090
without distinctions of background

639
00:33:17,220 --> 00:33:18,940
or struggles of the inner chambers.

640
00:33:28,700 --> 00:33:29,540
Jiangli,

641
00:33:29,820 --> 00:33:30,860
what are you doing?

642
00:33:31,340 --> 00:33:32,460
You've even made a tomb

643
00:33:32,460 --> 00:33:33,500
for this ungrateful girl.

644
00:33:34,220 --> 00:33:35,060
Shen Zhengshan,

645
00:33:35,740 --> 00:33:37,020
