646
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:38,860
You should say goodbye to her.

647
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:40,220
No, no, no.

648
00:33:40,420 --> 00:33:42,060
My family has no such criminal.

649
00:33:42,740 --> 00:33:43,800
She poisoned the princess

650
00:33:44,020 --> 00:33:45,340
and tried to burn a consort.

651
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:46,780
I never imagined

652
00:33:47,180 --> 00:33:48,160
she could be so vicious.

653
00:33:48,740 --> 00:33:49,580
Lord Shen,

654
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:51,340
the deceased has gone.

655
00:33:51,820 --> 00:33:52,660
You should be

656
00:33:53,020 --> 00:33:54,420
more careful with your words.

657
00:33:55,900 --> 00:33:57,420
Yes, Master Jingming.

658
00:33:57,740 --> 00:33:59,380
Jiangli is so kind.

659
00:33:59,740 --> 00:34:01,420
She even made her a tomb

660
00:34:01,620 --> 00:34:02,560
to pay respects to her.

661
00:34:03,660 --> 00:34:04,500
Shen Zhengshan,

662
00:34:05,420 --> 00:34:07,100
as her father, it's what you should do.

663
00:34:08,060 --> 00:34:09,340
Have you ever thought about why

664
00:34:09,580 --> 00:34:10,420
my mother,

665
00:34:10,620 --> 00:34:11,460
Zou,

666
00:34:11,620 --> 00:34:13,100
and Qilan ended up like this??

667
00:34:13,860 --> 00:34:15,380
How would I know?

668
00:34:15,900 --> 00:34:17,940
Our family has had no luck.

669
00:34:18,860 --> 00:34:20,700
I was fulfilling my official duties,

670
00:34:21,220 --> 00:34:23,020
drinking and singing happily,

671
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:25,500
and then everything suddenly changed.

672
00:34:26,180 --> 00:34:28,300
They left me one by one,

673
00:34:28,620 --> 00:34:31,780
leaving me to bury my own family.

674
00:34:35,460 --> 00:34:36,340
Let me tell you.

675
00:34:37,180 --> 00:34:38,020
It's because of you.

676
00:34:38,220 --> 00:34:40,220
You favored your concubines
instead of your wife,

677
00:34:40,260 --> 00:34:41,640
only caring for your own interests.

678
00:34:41,820 --> 00:34:42,660
At home,

679
00:34:42,820 --> 00:34:44,380
you never acted like a husband

680
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,500
or father.

681
00:34:46,220 --> 00:34:47,340
You're selfish.

682
00:34:47,700 --> 00:34:49,660
Whenever something happens,
you stir up trouble.

683
00:34:50,740 --> 00:34:53,220
You've ruined our family's morals.

684
00:34:53,740 --> 00:34:55,860
That's why they ended up like this.

685
00:34:56,180 --> 00:34:57,020
Yes, yes,

686
00:34:57,380 --> 00:34:58,420
You're right.

687
00:34:58,740 --> 00:35:00,500
But it's all in the past now.

688
00:35:01,340 --> 00:35:03,660
Now, only two of us
are left in the family.

689
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:05,020
From now on,

690
00:35:05,020 --> 00:35:06,300
you're my only hope.

691
00:35:08,980 --> 00:35:09,820
Lord Shen,

692
00:35:10,940 --> 00:35:12,540
I don't think you can count on me.

693
00:35:12,740 --> 00:35:14,060
Take care of yourself.

694
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:15,420
Jiangli,

695
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:16,480
what do you mean by that?

696
00:35:17,100 --> 00:35:18,340
I'm your father!

697
00:35:18,940 --> 00:35:19,910
- Jiangli.
- Jiangli,

698
00:35:20,270 --> 00:35:21,830
you will always have Yanyan and me.

699
00:35:21,980 --> 00:35:24,180
You are my daughter.

700
00:35:24,580 --> 00:35:25,500
You've all gone.

701
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:26,340
Why don't you

702
00:35:26,620 --> 00:35:28,060
move back to my house?

703
00:35:29,410 --> 00:35:30,550
Come back.

704
00:35:32,340 --> 00:35:33,180
Your Grace,

705
00:35:33,540 --> 00:35:35,020
you've been staying here for so long.

706
00:35:35,060 --> 00:35:37,180
You must be missing the scenery
of your hometown.

707
00:35:39,860 --> 00:35:40,700
Why don't we

708
00:35:41,060 --> 00:35:43,180
