709
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:44,820
Hunting?

710
00:35:46,020 --> 00:35:47,220
Do you also hunt

711
00:35:47,620 --> 00:35:48,700
in Dongzhou?

712
00:35:48,940 --> 00:35:49,820
Of course.

713
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:51,660
In Dongzhou, men are skilled

714
00:35:51,940 --> 00:35:53,420
in both literature and martial arts,

715
00:35:53,420 --> 00:35:54,620
riding and archery.

716
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:55,640
Of course,

717
00:35:55,810 --> 00:35:56,940
we can hunt.

718
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:58,820
Master Jingxiu,

719
00:35:59,030 --> 00:36:01,020
I didn't expect you to be good at this.

720
00:36:01,740 --> 00:36:02,860
In that case,

721
00:36:03,180 --> 00:36:04,420
why don't we go for a contest

722
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:06,340
in a few days?

723
00:36:08,060 --> 00:36:09,620
What about today?

724
00:36:10,180 --> 00:36:11,380
The weather is great,

725
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:12,580
so how about today?

726
00:36:14,140 --> 00:36:15,060
Sure.

727
00:36:15,060 --> 00:36:17,300
Then let's invite the other two masters.

728
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,140
We'll go together.

729
00:36:20,820 --> 00:36:21,660
Well,

730
00:36:22,020 --> 00:36:24,460
Jingming should be busy with work.

731
00:36:24,460 --> 00:36:25,420
How about

732
00:36:25,780 --> 00:36:27,020
inviting Jingxing?

733
00:36:27,700 --> 00:36:28,540
Alright.

734
00:36:29,060 --> 00:36:30,660
Someone, prepare the horses.

735
00:36:36,140 --> 00:36:37,900
Young Master,
I have something to report.

736
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:39,100
As you instructed,

737
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:41,260
I've had people watch
Master Jingxiu's Mansion.

738
00:36:41,460 --> 00:36:42,380
Just now,

739
00:36:42,380 --> 00:36:43,520
the assassin who escaped

740
00:36:43,520 --> 00:36:45,060
disguised himself as a vegetable vendor

741
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:46,500
and entered Master Jingxiu's Mansion,

742
00:36:46,580 --> 00:36:47,900
so I rushed back to report.

743
00:36:49,260 --> 00:36:50,100
Got it.

744
00:36:50,780 --> 00:36:52,100
Do not act rashly.

745
00:36:53,060 --> 00:36:54,470
Yes. I'll take my leave.

746
00:37:01,180 --> 00:37:08,180
