to discuss.

750
00:37:12,980 --> 00:37:14,420
I won't have lunch at home today.

751
00:37:15,020 --> 00:37:15,860
It's so urgent?

752
00:37:15,980 --> 00:37:17,180
Do you want me to go with you?

753
00:37:18,380 --> 00:37:19,220
This matter

754
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:20,740
is still unclear.

755
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,220
I'll go by myself.

